summary: This document appears to be a lieutenant's log and daily activity report from the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) in New York for August 10, 2019, the day Jeffrey Epstein was found dead in his cell. It is marked as confidential and part of the SDNY case files.

keyFacts: The document is a confidential lieutenant's log and daily activity report from the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) dated August 10, 2019.
The date corresponds to the day Jeffrey Epstein was found dead in his cell.
The document is part of the Southern District of New York (SDNY) case files related to the Epstein investigation.
